{"tid":2422196,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"鼓勵員工Office講鬼故、開畫班 JobsDB香港CEO 　請人必問一條Q：你有咩特異功能？","createTime":"2021-02-25T04:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T07:26:14.000Z","uid":271829,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6df807d72bbaeb67aa9ff322afb057135360a55b","tid":2422196,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-n3V4w0EPsz8UjLwCG_c408RPuc=/1597x895/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V36ISFSJQBGRJCRJQW3JQF45VA.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-n3V4w0EPsz8UjLwCG_c408RPuc%3D%2F1597x895%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV36ISFSJQBGRJCRJQW3JQF45VA.PNG&h=c88d18a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJobsDB香港區行政總裁仇崑石認為，各行各業加快數碼轉型，企業要保持競爭力，須先建立員工的軟實力，辦公室正是一個關鍵場地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pxekL1j_Yqalv8l-YMKSNLL1VDo=/1589x893/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EWP3YHTQUJHQ7NRE7ATHXDXIRU.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpxekL1j_Yqalv8l-YMKSNLL1VDo%3D%2F1589x893%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEWP3YHTQUJHQ7NRE7ATHXDXIRU.PNG&h=63898295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辦公室三分之一佔地被劃作共享空間「Social Hub」，設有打機室、Nap Room。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Z_2QcAMbcpkui5xXI6bPfgyG_9g=/1587x892/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PV7UTK3HXJCY7I4PZNPH2DFPBU.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZ_2QcAMbcpkui5xXI6bPfgyG_9g%3D%2F1587x892%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPV7UTK3HXJCY7I4PZNPH2DFPBU.PNG&h=fe6bbcd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辦公室人人「Be Water」坐彈性辦公桌（Flexi-desk），就連CEO亦沒有獨立房。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n求職平台JobsDB常幫人找工作，但原來要加入這間公司亦殊不簡單，因每名新員工也會被CEO考問，「你有甚麼特異功能？」在JobsDB客戶服務部工作兩年的Casper笑言，當時他只說了喜歡畫畫和講鬼故，後來才知道CEO「起底」的用意，是為了知道員工的個人興趣。<br />\n<br />\nJobsDB香港區行政總裁仇崑石（Isaac）解釋，行業加快數碼轉型，企業要維持競爭力，必須了解員工的專長，將「特異功能」發揮在職場上，以助培養他們的軟技能（Soft Skills），包括協作、溝通及領導能力等，是應對知識型經濟的關鍵。為貫徹宗旨，JobsDB上月斥資8位數字搬新辦公室，主打「Jobs That Matter」理念，將三分之一（4000平方尺）佔地劃作共享空間「Social Hub」，為180名員工提供打機室、Nap Room（寢室）、Bar枱等。<br />\n<br />\nIsaac指出，共享空間鼓勵員工自發舉辦活動，例如講鬼故、開辦調酒、沖咖啡、瑜伽等工作坊，甚至手作市集。「每個人都有自己興趣，無論與工作是否相關，給予機會讓他們分享，甚至教同事，能彼此欣賞並建立自信，工作會開心很多，配合得更好。」<br />\n<br />\n辦公室不只是工作地方，同事交流亦相當重要。舉例，員工就有份投票決定會議室以香港山峰命名，如大帽山、獅子山等，又購入本地手工啤酒，讓大家疲累時Chill一翻。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210225/5PGACHXQMZBPVLPBS3DKAZPW7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210225%2F5PGACHXQMZBPVLPBS3DKAZPW7Y%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFeTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=9c8fcb17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210225%2F5PGACHXQMZBPVLPBS3DKAZPW7Y%2F&h=bd4f845d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210225/5PGACHXQMZBPVLPBS3DKAZPW7Y/</a>"},{"pid":"27f50ff342aa42bc23ca6efb4c46a2fa6cd3ad2f","tid":2422196,"uid":60535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工"},{"pid":"f62e4230019ffd2a42d6e985723573810f98df95","tid":2422196,"uid":83060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"周綺萍啲friend"},{"pid":"1cae0341ceb0ce5e891284d09910d1b45b545da3","tid":2422196,"uid":251168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"JobsDB香港區行政總裁<span class=\"red\">仇崑石</span>咁咁個名"},{"pid":"514f6d1ac58e01b44ddff41528e80f10d4c9d8e8","tid":2422196,"uid":349058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:50:57.000Z","msg":"可以順手壓多幾k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421bed651a5b7adbc4acbcb22271abb14d05f8c3","tid":2422196,"uid":88592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27f50ff342aa42bc23ca6efb4c46a2fa6cd3ad2f","tid":2422196,"uid":60535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:26:14.000Z","msg":"想知+1"}]}